Hair discrimination remains a source of racial injustice with serious economic consequences for Black People. The CROWN ACT corrects these racial injustices by making hair discrimination illegal.
👑👑👑👑👑👑👑👑👑👑👑👑👑
Currently, it is legal to discriminate against a person in the workplace or in schools because of their natural or protective hairstyle in all states except for California, New York, New Jersey, Virginia, Colorado, Washington, Maryland, Connecticut, Delaware, New Mexico, Nebraska, Nevada and Oregon. 👉🏾*CLICK THE LINK IN BIO to learn more and SIGN the petition.

#hair #naturalhair #protectivestyles #blackcurlmagic #blackgirlmagic #endracism #fbf #friday #fridayfeeling #fearlessfriday #loveisinthehair
